FT  01 OCT 93 / World News in Brief: Backing for Canary Wharf plan
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Unsecured creditors of Olympia &amp; York, the company which built Canary Wharf,
have given unanimous backing to a Pounds 1.1bn rescue plan for the London
Docklands complex. Their support clears the way for Canary Wharf to come out
of administration later this month.
